query:
SELECT t.id, t.name, ti.id as item_id, ti.itemText, ti.`order` 
FROM checklistTemplates t 
LEFT JOIN checklistTemplateItems ti ON t.id = ti.templateId 
WHERE t.name LIKE '%ทดสอบ%'
ORDER BY t.id, ti.`order`
